Por termos uma escola de desenvolvimento pessoal e técnico focado em dados e uma base com mais de 5000 analistas e engenheiros de dados, conseguimos ajudar empresas a encontrar profissionais de níveis júnior, pleno e sênior.

Lukka is a team of top-performing data experts that are transforming financial crypto data into easy-to-use information for businesses.

Founded in 2014, Lukka serves the most risk-mature businesses in the world with institutional data and SaaS solutions. As a global company, headquartered in the United States, Lukka bridges the gap between the complexities of blockchain data in a global crypto ecosystem with traditional business and reporting needs. Our customers include all types of businesses, both traditional and digital asset-native, including, but not limited to many of the largest banks in the world, digital asset/crypto exchanges, trading desks, CPA & accounting firms, fund and financial auditors, fund administrators, miners, pools, protocols, individuals, government agencies and tax authorities as they interact, manage, or provide services related to digital assets.

Risk maturity is built into Lukka’s culture and DNA. Lukka was the first in the industry to not only complete an AICPA Service Organization Controls (SOC) 1 Type II and AICPA SOC 2 Type II audits, but to build its products with these frameworks at the center of their design and architecture. Lukka has maintained SOC audits from a top 10 auditor for 6+ consecutive years and maintains the globally recognized data security-focused ISO/IEC-27001 certification, IOSCO Statement of Adherence to Financial Benchmarks, among others.

Products and Services include but are not limited to: 
- Full Trade Life Cycle Crypto/Token Market Data; 
- Enterprise SaaS for Financial
data management (collection, standardization, reconciliation, tax and accounting, crypto-sub ledger, compliance, AML, and bespoke reporting);
- Custom Reference Rates, Benchmarks, Index Creation, Calc Agent Services, NAV data;
- Blockchain Analytics, Investigations, Real time Wallet monitoring, Wallet and Transaction Level Analysis, Entity Due Diligence, Sanction Screening
- And Custom Enterprise and Core Banking Integrations

