Arbitrate is an intelligent technology platform that collates the cost of vehicles available for hire from the top 6 rental providers across the UK. The system contains 5+ years worth of information, with over 20m rows of data and 50,000 new rows collected every day. As a result, we can quickly generate robust, time-specific and geographically appropriate evidence to show the ‘going rate’, or the Basic Hire Rate (BHR), for the period of hire in question. Our customers can then use this information to help settle Credit Hire invoices at a fair and reasonable daily rate, based on demonstrable evidence.

We believe that we are different to the typical BHR defense in the following ways: 

• We provide a truly unique proposition in the marketplace, from data, service, technology and cost perspectives;
• We are the only automated data engine in the UK, covering the last 5 years;
• Our reports are contemporaneous, geographically appropriate and if required, court compliant;
• We can cover all daily rental scenarios, drawing from a vast and continuously increasing data set, constantly analysed for patterns and trends:
• We can configure the system and its outputs to meet with our clients' specific needs;
• We are ruthlessly focused on our customers, delivering first class customer service with a can-do attitude.

Oferecemos soluções inteligentes voltadas para maximização de resultados utilizando tecnologia da informação. 

Nossos produtos:
- Automatização de Processos (Robôs - RPA);
- Desenvolvimento de Sistemas Integradores;
- Business Intelligence (BI);
- Consultoria de Processos para Sistemas Integrados;
- Gerenciamento de Projetos de Inovação.

